# 💳 ATM Simulator (Java + MySQL)

This is a **Java-based ATM Simulator** project that uses **MySQL** as a backend database.  
It allows users to log in with their **card number** and **PIN**, then perform ATM operations such as:

- ✅ Login with card & PIN  
- 💵 Deposit money  
- 🏧 Withdraw money  
- 📊 Check account balance  
- 🧾 View mini statement  

---

## 🚀 Technologies Used
- **Java 17+**
- **MySQL 8+**
- **JDBC (MySQL Connector 9.4.0)**

---

## 📂 Project Structure
atm-simulator-mysql/
│
├── src/
│ ├── Main.java
│ ├── Account.java
│ ├── ATMService.java
│ ├── Menu.java
│ └── DatabaseManager.java
│
├── lib/
│ └── mysql-connector-j-9.4.0.jar
│
├── db/   
#compiling the program-javac -cp "lib/mysql-connector-j-9.4.0.jar;src" src/*.java -d out
#run the code-java -cp "lib/mysql-connector-j-9.4.0.jar;out" Main
│ └── atm.sql # Database schema & sample data  
│
├── out/ # Compiled classes (after build)
│
└── README.md
